-- Artifact Piece 3 --

The third and final piece of the artifact, other than that which the 
Predacons had, appeared up north, above the current location of the 
magnetic north pole. It was still warm from being used, and being 
teleported, so when it hit the ice, it melted down a bit. The water 
which it melted and froze into ice, leaving the artifact piece 
covered by a few feet of ice.
